This project is help students create an XSD.

The sales example is done incrementatlly.
Begin with version A of the XML and XSD.
Study the files.
Then, in package explorer, double-click version A of the sales Example.
Right-click and select Validate XML. The file will be validated.
Then study and validate version B then C ....

A final version of the sales XML and XSD are provided.

There are other examples in other folders.

I hope you have fun defining your schema !

Regards,
Phil "javaman" Stang



